title: Tiffany Stained Glass Daffodil Earrings
description:
Louis Comfort Tiffany and his artisans captured the beauty and nuance of the natural world with their innovative leaded glass pieces. Tiffany designer Clara Driscoll provided the inspiration for these daffodil earrings, from the collection of the New York Historical Society. Ships nicely boxed and ready for gifting.

  • Dimensions: 2 in.
  • Materials: solid brass, giclee print, gold plated ear wire
